(text "NOTE: no wires used - connectivity is via matching label names (valid KiCad practice)." (at 20.32 219.71 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 5698b271-0c0e-56cb-a933-05a643e922f5))
(text "The real pack already has a protection-only BMS; U1/Q1/Q2 are optional/DNP unless a bare-cell pack is used." (at 20.32 226.06 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 165c9780-7afd-59c6-8f4b-b17c55fe4d24))
(text "RS1 remains populated as the BQ34Z100-G1 low-side current shunt; Kelvin route SRP/SRN per TI layout guidance." (at 20.32 232.41 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 0759d61c-0ad3-587e-85cc-703e4df622d6))
(text "U10 pinout is verified against TI Table 5-1; divider 215k/16.5k gives about 0.90V at 12.6V full-charge 3S." (at 20.32 237.49 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 0e87b1e8-d09a-565d-8633-b73136a8f296))
(text "TS1/TS2/TS3/FG_TS use independent thermistor dividers per-IC (not shared) per design decision." (at 20.32 243.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid e7f31cc4-7451-59bc-8dd5-22e0b88dd283))
(text "Charger I2C/INT/QON/CE pull-ups use MCU_3V3 so STM32 pins never see REGN-level logic." (at 20.32 250.19 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 35699f37-d404-5932-baaa-421b1a372268))
(text "U2 ILIM_HIZ divider sets about 3A input-current clamp from REGN; PROG selects 3S/1.5MHz POR defaults." (at 20.32 256.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 4dce50b2-b412-52ab-aeea-6709456c81a0))
(text "J190 is shared: default random-DC mode populates D191 to U2; solar mode populates D8/U3 MPPT option." (at 20.32 264.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ae95599f-5d0c-5397-a99d-53c6e2139acd))
(text "If solar option is used, U3 starts at 18V nominal MPP, 12.6V 3S regulation, and 1A solar charge current." (at 20.32 271.78 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ef372226-4e5e-5e34-b305-510e6ff35e23))
(text "Default BOM should not populate D8 with D191; choose random-DC charger input or solar MPPT behavior for J190." (at 20.32 279.4 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 2b7031b6-ebaa-5b02-8d05-349a6e388e57))
(text "AUX_DC_ADC lets EC firmware detect random bench/DC inputs and reduce BQ25798 input current if the source droops." (at 20.32 287.02 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 975e2269-e797-5c90-bdf6-5151dd20ac39))
(text "U2 VAC1/VAC2 tie to VBUS_COMBINED in no-external-mux mode; ACDRV1/2 go to GND." (at 20.32 294.64 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 990831b5-7f04-5ec1-b5d3-ff46992a24ec))
(text "SDRV has 1nF to GND because the ship FET is unused in this first integrated laptop spin." (at 20.32 302.26 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid da7b7e61-eaa2-560c-a6a1-2fdf409250b9))
(text "DNP Q1/Q2 candidate: Infineon IPD90N04S4L-04, 40V 3.8mR DPAK, active/preferred, pin 1=G 2=D/tab 3=S." (at 20.32 309.88 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d9ac5598-611b-5fbc-b995-9569cb94c58c))
(text "DNP Q3/Q4 candidate: Infineon IPD50N04S4L-08, 40V 7.3mR DPAK, lower Qg for BQ24650 6V gate drive." (at 20.32 317.5 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c3cd3ce8-ed6d-5144-a355-48259eb77bd8))
